Mo Salah Fan Website

This repository contains the source code for a fan website dedicated to Mohamed Salah, the renowned Egyptian professional footballer. The website is part of a Code Institute project and showcases various aspects of Salah's career and contributions, including his biography, achievements, records, and a gallery of memorable moments.

