Installation

To run this project locally, follow these steps:

Clone the repository:

git clone https://github.com/Omar6688/Salah.git

Navigate to the project directory:

cd Salah

Open the index.html file in your preferred web browser.

Testing

This project has been tested for:

Cross-Browser Compatibility: Ensuring consistent performance on modern web browsers like Chrome, Firefox, Safari, and Edge.

